This work (all text, images, cover art, build scripts and generated
artifacts in this repository — the "Work") is licensed for EDUCATIONAL
and RESEARCH purposes only.

Subject to that limit, any person may, free of charge:
  1. read, download and reproduce the Work;
  2. distribute or quote it for personal study, teaching, or academic
     research, provided this license notice and attribution to the
     original authors are retained.

The following require the authors' prior written permission:
  • commercial use (sale, paid courses, ad revenue, commercial
    publishing, etc.);
  • repackaging the Work or substantial portions as a product or
    service for public distribution.

Notice:
  • The Work is an organization and critical annotation of public
    technical topics (knowledge distillation, computer-use agents,
    caching). Product names such as Fable 5, Mythos, Qwythos and
    Aluminium OS — wherever flagged "⚠️ Authenticity Caveat" — cannot
    be verified by this book and should be read as narrative symbols or
    plausible engineering hypotheses, representing no official position
    of any real product.
  • All benefit, score, latency and cost figures are illustrative upper
    bounds or scenario projections, not guarantees.
  • Any description of unauthorized capability extraction, bypassing
    access controls, or removing safety alignment is RISK DISCLOSURE
    ONLY and is not operational advice; the corresponding operational
    material (jailbreak banks, de-censorship recipes, vendor-defense
    bypass scripts) is deliberately NOT included.
  • The Work is provided "AS IS", without warranty of any kind. The
    authors are not liable for any damages arising from its use.

